        ))}
      </div>

      <CalloutBox type="info" class="mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Property Value Protection</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Real estate data shows homes with visible settlement signs sell for 15-25% below market value, 
